No. —.

Ennis et al. v. Evans et al.

The application for a stay of the execution and enforcement of the judgments of the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit presented to Mr. Justice Brennan, and by *803him referred to the Court, is denied.

Januar D. Bove, Jr., Attorney General of Delaware, and James M. Tunnell, Jr. for applicants.
